###
### MCP Echo Server - HTTP Requests for Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### Documentation: FastMCP Echo Server endpoints for inspecting server behaviors
###

### 1. SIMPLE ECHO TEST
### Test: Echo a simple greeting message
POST http://localhost:8000/api/tools/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "arguments": {
    "message": "Hello, World!"
  }
}

###

### 2. ECHO EMPTY STRING
### Test: Echo behavior with empty string input
POST http://localhost:8000/api/tools/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "arguments": {
    "message": ""
  }
}

###

### 3. ECHO WITH SPECIAL CHARACTERS
### Test: Echo preserves special characters, newlines, and tabs
POST http://localhost:8000/api/tools/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "arguments": {
    "message": "Line 1\nLine 2\tTabbed\n\"Quoted\" text"
  }
}

