### 19. VERIFY RESPONSE FORMAT
### Test: Verify echo response contains required fields
### Expected response structure:
###   - content: array of content objects
###   - isError: boolean flag
###   - content[].type: "text"
###   - content[].text: echoed message
POST http://localhost:8000/api/tools/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "arguments": {
    "message": "Test response format validation"
  }
}

